1.6
log
@use fancy .In macro for includes. from Jan Klemkow. ok jmc schwarze
@
text
@.\"	$OpenBSD: login.3,v 1.5 2007/05/31 19:19:38 jmc Exp $
.\"
.\" Copyright (c) 1995
.\"	The Regents of the University of California.  All rights reserved.
